<br>
I just wanted to say that, regardless of my comments about what I feel to be the fact that EQ is not being left behind in any way, shape or form, I am also aware that the poll showed that a large percentage of you think that it is.  Obviously, I don't want you to have that impression, and there are probably a few things we can do to change that.<br>
<br>
So how about this, let's see what we can do over the next few months to change your minds.  Maybe we can have another poll then and see how it goes.<br>
<br>
Thanks for the information and the conversation.<br>
